  "title": "Ecommerce Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to use the computer to handle fulfillment of orders</li>\n  <li>Perform Labeling, picking, packing and sorting of products</li>\n  <li>Ensure high accuracy of work</li>\n  <li>Stock Taking</li>\n  <li>Provide assistance &amp; support within the Ecommerce department</li>\n  <li>Handle Customer service professionally</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for long-term career progression</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to work overseas</li>\n  <li>Oppostunities to work in sales</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Positive attitude, responsible, self-motivated and willing to learn</li>\n  <li>We are looking for highly motivated personnel that are in line with our vision and is keen to contribute to a rapidly growing company.</li>\n  <li>We are currently looking for personnel on weekend saturday/sunday.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Additional Considerations:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Higher educational certifications(eg. Diploma/Degree) are also welcome and pay will be scaled according to job scope and qualifications.</li>\n  <li>Both Part time/Full time are welcome to apply.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
